quran[30{c,v,t}:
74,18,is ne socha aur kuch baat bananay ki koshish ki
74,19,"to khuda ki maar is par, kaisi baat bananay ki koshish ki"
74,20,"haan, khuda ki maar uss par, kaisi baat bananay ki koshish ki"
74,21,phir ( logon ki taraf ) dekha
74,22,phir peshani sukerri aur mun banaya
74,23,phir palta aur taqqabur mein par gaya
74,24,aakhir kaar bola ke yeh kuch nahi hai magar aik jaadoo jo pehlay se chala aa raha hai
74,25,yeh to yeh aik insani kalaam hai
74,26,anqareeb mein usay dozakh mein jhonk dun ga
74,27,aur tum kya jano ke kya hai woh dozakh ?
74,28,nah baqi rakhay nah chhorey
74,29,khaal jhulas dainay wali
74,30,Anees karkun uss par muqarrar hain
74,31,"hum ne dozakh ke yeh karkun farishtay banaye hain, aur un ki tadaad ko kafiroon ke liye fitnah bana diya hai, taakay ahal kitaab ko yaqeen aa jaye aur imaan laane walon ka imaan barhay, aur ahal kitaab aur momnin kisi shak mein nah rahen, aur dil ke bemaar aur kufar yeh kahin ke bhala Allah ka iss ajeeb baat se kya matlab ho sakta hai iss terhan Allah jisay chahta hai gumraah kar deta hai aur jisay chahta hai hadaayat bakhash deta hai aur tairay rab ke lashkaron ko khud uss ke siwa koi nahi jaanta aur is dozakh ka zikar iss ke siwa kisi gharz ke liye nahi kya gaya hai ke logon ko is se nasiyaat ho"
74,32,"hargiz nahi, qasam hai chaand ki"
74,33,aur raat ki jabkay woh palatti hai
74,34,aur subah ki jabkay woh roshan hoti hai
74,35,yeh dozakh bhi barri cheezon mein se aik hai
74,36,insanon ke liye darawa
74,37,tum mein se har uss shakhs ke liye darawa jo agay barhna chahay ya peechay reh jana chahay
74,38,"har mutnaqas, apne ksb ke badlay rehan hai"
74,39,dayen baazu walon ke siwa
74,40,"jojannaton mein hon ge wahan woh ,"
74,41,mujrimon se poucheen ge
74,42,""" tumhe kya cheez dozakh mein le gayi? """
74,43,"woh kahin ge"" hum namaz parhnay walon mein se nah thay"
74,44,aur maskeen ko khana nahi khelate thay
74,45,aur haq ke khilaaf baatein bananay walon ke sath mil kar hum bhi baatein bananay lagtay thay
74,46,aur roz jaza ko jhoot qarar dete thay
74,47,"yahan taq ke hamein uss yakeeni cheez se Sabiqa paish aa gaya """
